    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were scoped out as not applicable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The hemolysis prediction methodology is supported by the FDA benchmark dataset and the peer-reviewed validation framework described in the referenced literature. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) was met across all five operating conditions. The assessment team concludes that the computational model provides adequate credibility for the intended COU.",
